hopobject.body: Are you a student? ekospharma.com.br Ok for me, noone is ever going to replace or has been as good as David Tennant as the doctor and I have watched them all! I did kind of like Matt Smith's originality though. First impressions of the new Doctor are not very favourable but I suppose we should give him the chance. Personally his face as a Time Lord just doesn't fit into the role as I perceive it and I don't fancy watching him.....
